Business Brief -- Ameriwood Industries:
   Atlantis Motion to Dismiss
   Firm's Charges Is Set Back
Atlantis has also asked the court to withdraw a suit it
filed against Ameriwood and its other major shareholders.
Ameriwood, which is based in Grand Rapids, Mich., and the
other defendants in that case are asking the court to award
them $500,000 in costs related to the suit now being
withdrawn.
   Ameriwood said attempts to resolve the litigation with
Atlantis by purchasing its Ameriwood shares weren't
successful and negotiations have been terminated.